---

<Layout title="Scarborough Airbnb Management" description="Expert Airbnb management in Scarborough. We manage properties near Scarborough Town Centre, the Bluffs, Agincourt & Rouge Valley. 10-15% fees, 9-min response.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1><span class="highlight">Scarborough Airbnb Management</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">From the Bluffs to the Zoo - untapped Airbnb potential</p>

      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">$3,200+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Avg Monthly Revenue</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">78%+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Avg Occupancy Rate</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">10-15%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Management Fee</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">See How Much Your Scarborough Property Can Earn</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section neighborhoods">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Scarborough Neighborhoods We Serve</h2>
        <p>Diverse communities with unique appeal</p>
      </div>
      <div class="neighborhoods-grid">
        {neighborhoods.map(n => (
          <div class="neighborhood-card">
            <h3>{n.icon} {n.name}</h3>
            <p>{n.description}</p>
            <div class="avg-revenue">Avg Revenue: {n.revenue}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bylaws-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Scarborough Short-Term Rental Bylaws</h2>
        <p>What Scarborough property owners need to know</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bylaws-content">
        <div class="bylaws-grid">
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>Registration Required</h3>
            <p>All short-term rentals in Toronto (including Scarborough) must be registered with the City. We can help you navigate the registration process. <a href="https://www.toronto.ca/community-people/housing-shelter/rental-housing-tenant-information/short-term-rentals/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Register on the City of Toronto website</a>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>Principal Residence Rule</h3>
            <p>You can only operate a short-term rental in your principal residence. This is the home where you live and receive mail, file taxes, etc.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>180-Night Annual Limit</h3>
            <p>Entire-home rentals are limited to 180 nights per year. However, mid-term rentals (stays of 28 days or more) do not count toward this limit. Partial unit rentals have some exemptions to allow for more than 180 nights per year.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>Municipal Accommodation Tax</h3>
            <p>A Municipal Accommodation Tax (MAT) applies to all short-term rentals. Platforms like Airbnb collect and remit this automatically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section why-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Scarborough: The Untapped Opportunity</h2>
        <p>Less competition, unique attractions, strong returns</p>
      </div>
      <div class="opportunity-content">
        <p>While downtown Toronto is saturated with Airbnbs, Scarborough remains underserved. Fewer listings mean less competition, and unique attractions like the Bluffs, Zoo, and Rouge Park draw visitors year-round. Properties here often outperform expectations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="opportunity-stats">
        <div class="opp-stat">
          <div class="number">40%</div>
          <div class="label">Less Competition Than Downtown</div>
        </div>
        <div class="opp-stat">
          <div class="number">2.7M</div>
          <div class="label">Annual Zoo Visitors</div>
        </div>
        <div class="opp-stat">
          <div class="number">15km</div>
          <div class="label">Of Bluffs Shoreline</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section services-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Full-Service Scarborough Management</h2>
        <p>Everything included at 10-15%</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services-grid">
        {services.map(service => (
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="service-check">‚úì</span>
            <span>{service}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Own a Scarborough Property?</h2>
        <p>Get a free analysis showing how much your Bluffs, Town Centre, or Rouge Valley property could earn with Airbnb.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-large">Get Your Free Analysis</a>
        <p class="cta-note">Free consultation - No obligation - Results in 24 hours</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-background-alt) 0%, var(--color-background) 100%);
    padding: 8rem 0 6rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: -2rem;
  }

  .location-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero .highlight { color: var(--color-primary); }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .stat { text-align: center; }
  .stat-number { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .stat-label { color: var(--color-text-light); font-size: 0.9rem; }

  .neighborhoods-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .neighborhood-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border-top: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .neighborhood-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }
  .neighborhood-card h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .neighborhood-card p { color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; }

  .avg-revenue {
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .bylaws-section { background: var(--color-background-alt); }

  .bylaws-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .bylaw-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .bylaw-card h3 { color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .bylaw-card p { color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.7; }
  .bylaw-card a { color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: underline; }
  .bylaw-card a:hover { color: var(--color-primary-dark); }

  .bylaws-cta {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .bylaws-cta p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }

  .why-section {
    background: var(--color-primary-dark);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .why-section .section-header h2 { color: white; }
  .why-section .section-header p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); }

  .opportunity-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .opportunity-content p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .opportunity-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .opp-stat {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .opp-stat .number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #C9A961;
  }

  .opp-stat .label {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .services-section { background: var(--color-background-alt); }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .service-item {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .service-check { color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; }

  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 100%);
    padding: 5rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-content h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-content > p { font-size: 1.25rem; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .cta-section .btn { background: white; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .cta-section .btn:hover { background: var(--color-background-alt); }
  .cta-note { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.9; }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .neighborhoods-grid, .services-grid, .opportunity-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .bylaws-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .hero-stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }
    .neighborhoods-grid, .services-grid, .opportunity-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
